rows.label: tlk47100071_01_msg0001
rows.name:
What? You tryin' to rub my tummy
like a Nopon or sumfing?

rows.label: tlk47100071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Eh? You can understand me?!
Heh, life's full o' surprises.

rows.label: tlk47100071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, tell those brats something for
me, would ya?

rows.label: tlk47100071_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Tell 'em to lay off my tails. If they're
gonna pet me at all, pet me on the
'ead. That's the way I like it.
